data.text:
Michael B. Hensley, age 77, of Clearwater, passed away on Sunday, Jan. 28, 2024.

He was preceded in death by his son, Thomas Hensley; parents, Arvel “Slim” and Nora Belle (Patterson) Hensley; and brother, Stephen Hensley.

Survivors include his wife, Christy Hensley; son, David Hensley of Kansas City, Mo.; and sister, Melissa Petzschler of Wichita.

In lieu of flowers, memorials may be made to the Kansas Humane Society, 3313 N. Hillside, Wichita, KS 67219.

Leave online condolences with Webb-Shinkle Mortuary, www.wsmortuary.com.
